comment4.target=void\ collisionCheck()
comment4.text=\r\n\ Checks\ if\ the\ player\ is\ touching\ an\ obstacle\ and\ which\ direction\ the\ player\ is\ facing,\ then\ moves\ the\ player\ in\ the\ opposite\ direction.\ The\ opposite\ direction\ movement\ cancels\ out\ any\ keyboard\ entries,\ so\ the\ player\ does\ not\ move.\r\n
comment5.params=
comment5.target=void\ entityCheck()
comment5.text=\r\n\ Checks\ for\ touching\ entities.\ If\ an\ Entity\ is\ being\ touched,\ the\ method\ will\ play\ the\ corresponding\ sound\ and\ adjust\ the\ correct\ stat,\ before\ removing\ the\ Entity\ from\ the\ world.\r\n
comment6.params=
comment6.target=boolean\ isReady()
comment6.text=\r\n\ Called\ to\ check\ if\ the\ player\ has\ inputted\ on\ their\ keyboard.\ Villains\ will\ not\ attack\ until\ this\ method\ returns\ true.\r\n\ @return\ Whether\ the\ player\ is\ ready.\r\n
