comment7.text=\r\n\ Reports\ a\ specific\ player\ stat.\r\n\ @param\ stat\ The\ name\ of\ the\ variable\ to\ be\ returned\ in\ the\ method.\r\n\ @return\ An\ integer\ stat\ of\ the\ player\ specified\ in\ the\ parameter\ 'stat'.\ \r\n
